<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= titulo %></title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f0f5ff;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 30px auto;
        background: white;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3c72, #2a5298);
        color: white;
        padding: 20px 30px;
        margin: -30px -30px 30px -30px;
        border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        text-align: center;
      }
      h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 32px;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      }
      .card {
        background: #f9fbff;
        border-left: 4px solid #3a6eff;
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 25px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }
      .card:hover {
        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }
      .card h2 {
        color: #1e3c72;
        margin-top: 0;
        font-size: 24px;
      }
      .card h3 {
        color: #2a5298;
        margin-top: 0;
        font-size: 20px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #e1e8ff;
        padding-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .code {
        background: #eef2ff;
        border: 1px solid #d0d9ff;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
        overflow-x: auto;
        color: #2a5298;
      }
      ul {
        padding-left: 20px;
      }
      li {
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }
      strong {
        color: #1e3c72;
      }
      .btn-primary {
        display: block;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3a6eff, #1e3c72);
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 15px 30px;
        border-radius: 50px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin: 30px auto 10px;
        max-width: 400px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(42, 82, 152, 0.3);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }
      .btn-primary:hover {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4a7eff, #2a5298);
        box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(42, 82, 152, 0.4);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }
      .api-endpoints {
        background-color: #e6edff;
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 5px 15px;
      }
      .button-container {
        display: flex;
        gap: 20px;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-top: 30px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <header>
        <h1><%= titulo %></h1>
      </header>

      <div class="card">
        <h2><%= mensagem %></h2>
        <p>
          Este é o sistema de gerenciamento de reservas de salas do Inteli. Use
          nossa plataforma para agendar salas para reuniões, estudos e eventos
          de forma simples e eficiente.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Configuração do Banco de Dados</h3>
        <p>
          Para criar as tabelas necessárias, execute o script de inicialização
          usando:
        </p>
        <div class="code">node scripts/runSQLScript.js</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Endpoints da API</h3>
        <div class="api-endpoints">
          <ul>
            <li>
              <strong>GET /api/reservas</strong> - Listar todas as reservas
            </li>
            <li><strong>POST /api/reservas</strong> - Criar nova reserva</li>
            <li><strong>PUT /api/reservas/:id</strong> - Atualizar reserva</li>
            <li>
              <strong>DELETE /api/reservas/:id</strong> - Cancelar reserva
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>GET /api/reservas/usuario/:nome</strong> - Listar reservas
              de um usuário
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>GET /api/reservas/salas</strong> - Listar todas as salas
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="button-container">
        <a href="/salas-view" class="btn-primary">Ver Salas Disponíveis</a>
        <a href="/reservas-view" class="btn-primary">Gerenciar Reservas</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
